flowchart LR
    A[Top Bar] --> B[Workbench Shell]

    B --> C[Left Sidebar]
    B --> D[Right Chat Workspace]

    C --> E[Upper 60%: Projects]
    C --> F[Lower 40%: Upload Zone]

    E --> G[Plus Icon: Add Project]
    E --> H[Edit Icon: Toggle Edit Mode]
    E --> I[Project Rows]
    I --> J[Expandable File Tree]
    I --> K[Double-click or keyboard action selects project]
    H --> L[Per-row Edit/Delete Actions]

    F --> M[Drag and Drop Files]
    F --> N[Click to Select Files]
    M --> O[Upload to Active Project]
    N --> O

    D --> P{Conversation started?}
    P -->|No| Q[Centered Title + Translucent Composer]
    P -->|Yes| R[Conversation Area]
    R --> S[Assistant Answers]
    S --> T[Citations]
    S --> U[Feedback Controls]
    R --> V[Composer near bottom]

    D --> W[Floating Retrieval Button]
    W --> X[Retrieval Playground Route]

    subgraph ProjectContext[Active Project Context]
        K
        O
        R
        X
    end

    ProjectContext -. all API calls include .-> Y[project_id]
